WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 5=

02:01.820 --> 02:02.770
It's been three days.

02:04.660 --> 02:05.790
You haven't figured it out?

02:31.940 --> 02:32.780
Yuanfeng.

02:34.340 --> 02:35.760
Did you go to Chang Fort that night?

02:36.490 --> 02:37.690
Chang Ning, don't do this.

02:39.190 --> 02:40.080
Mr. Chang,

02:40.390 --> 02:41.450
look at Yuanfeng now.

02:41.450 --> 02:42.780
Why push him?

02:42.880 --> 02:43.760
Tell me.

02:59.030 --> 02:59.870
Yuanfeng...

03:00.850 --> 03:01.690
Yuanfeng...

03:05.910 --> 03:06.770
Where's Ms. Luo?

03:08.540 --> 03:09.380
Yes.

03:24.940 --> 03:25.780
Yuanying,

03:26.890 --> 03:28.290
you've been avenged.

03:29.390 --> 03:30.850
You can rest easy.

03:38.830 --> 03:40.560
♪In days gone by♪

03:40.870 --> 03:42.420
♪Willows swayed gently♪

03:42.720 --> 03:45.470
♪I first saw you in the dimness♪

03:46.440 --> 03:47.630
♪Amid the vast crowd♪

03:47.640 --> 03:49.110
♪A fleeting glance♪

03:49.280 --> 03:50.190
♪And then♪

03:50.200 --> 03:53.150
♪Love consumed me♪

03:53.960 --> 03:55.510
♪Now I think of you♪

03:55.910 --> 03:57.550
♪Snow and rain fall thickly♪

03:57.810 --> 03:59.150
♪Alas, we parted♪

03:59.160 --> 04:01.350
♪Longing for your return♪

04:01.480 --> 04:02.430
♪Moon waxes and wanes♪

04:02.440 --> 04:03.910
♪Letters can't convey my thoughts♪

04:03.920 --> 04:04.950
♪Scattered petals♪

04:04.960 --> 04:07.190
♪Cover the ground♪

04:07.380 --> 04:08.220
Yuanying.

04:08.250 --> 04:10.510
♪Such should be our meeting♪

04:10.690 --> 04:12.720
♪Golden wind brushes the jade dew♪

04:12.740 --> 04:13.850
Let's go home.

04:15.390 --> 04:18.110
♪Half shy, half joyful♪

04:18.210 --> 04:22.200
♪Wanting to leave yet lingering♪

04:22.860 --> 04:25.560
♪Such should be our meeting♪

04:25.740 --> 04:30.090
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

04:30.250 --> 04:32.970
♪Alas, peach blossoms have fallen♪

04:33.210 --> 04:39.090
♪Tears are like pearls♪

04:41.460 --> 04:43.680
♪Such should be♪

04:47.530 --> 04:49.180
Ms. Luo went to Chang Fort,

04:50.480 --> 04:52.070
so you recognized her early.

04:55.670 --> 04:56.720
Why didn't you tell me?

04:59.860 --> 05:00.820
Why did you protect her?

05:01.420 --> 05:02.260
What do you want?

05:03.620 --> 05:05.413
She wants to expose
Qiu Yuanfeng's true face.

05:06.340 --> 05:07.300
I must help her.

05:12.340 --> 05:13.900
Ms. Luo shouldn't have ended like that.

05:14.340 --> 05:15.180
If I could...

05:15.180 --> 05:16.660
She used Thunderstorm so close to him.

05:17.900 --> 05:18.860
She was ready

05:18.860 --> 05:20.580
to die with Qiu Yuanfeng.

05:21.066 --> 05:22.179
No one could've stopped her.

05:23.300 --> 05:25.020
We will remember the story

05:26.060 --> 05:26.980
of Ms. Luo and Mr. Wu.

05:29.300 --> 05:30.340
So will the world.

05:30.700 --> 05:31.660
But what use is that?

05:33.180 --> 05:34.460
In the end, it's all in vain.

05:39.620 --> 05:40.620
Mr. Wu,

05:42.340 --> 05:43.220
my aunt,

05:44.540 --> 05:45.620
and Uncle Chang.

05:47.020 --> 05:48.780
They shed blood for Jianghu.

05:49.540 --> 05:50.380
And the result?

05:53.180 --> 05:54.446
I never wanted to enter Jianghu,

05:56.180 --> 05:57.620
but as soon as I stepped outside,

06:00.740 --> 06:01.740
it was Jianghu.

06:03.580 --> 06:05.340
Fate is cruel, treating all as equals.

06:07.300 --> 06:08.140
You can choose

06:08.580 --> 06:09.420
to change your fate

06:10.340 --> 06:11.460
or do nothing.

06:13.620 --> 06:14.660
You can choose to avenge

06:15.940 --> 06:17.380
and vent grievances.

06:19.900 --> 06:21.140
This was their choice.

07:02.060 --> 07:02.900
Lei Xiuming,

07:03.933 --> 07:05.793
I can understand your absence
at the memorial,

07:06.700 --> 07:08.940
but today, you didn't attend Yuanrong

07:09.300 --> 07:10.140
and Wu's funeral?

07:11.340 --> 07:12.700
Death is like a snuffed lamp.

07:13.700 --> 07:14.760
What's the point of going?

07:15.900 --> 07:17.620
Besides, it's a cenotaph.

07:17.860 --> 07:18.940
So what?

07:19.620 --> 07:20.460
Lei Xiuming,

07:20.540 --> 07:21.700
you're still alive.

07:22.140 --> 07:23.380
Have you forgotten the time

07:23.380 --> 07:24.620
we drank from the same bowl?

07:25.100 --> 07:26.340
Breeze.

07:38.460 --> 07:39.300
Let's drink Breeze

07:39.460 --> 07:40.580
and enjoy ourselves.

07:41.140 --> 07:42.540
Enjoy!

07:43.420 --> 07:44.700
Come on, cheers!

07:47.180 --> 07:48.060
Come on, drink!

07:48.060 --> 07:48.910
Come on.

07:48.910 --> 07:50.070
Zhao said Yuanrong

07:51.780 --> 07:54.020
went to the wine cellar
before the memorial

07:56.740 --> 07:58.300
to find Breeze.

08:09.180 --> 08:10.460
Good!

08:11.540 --> 08:12.380
I haven't forgotten.

08:14.540 --> 08:15.940
But my martial arts are ruined.

08:17.700 --> 08:18.900
Other than catching my breath,

08:18.900 --> 08:19.940
what else can I do?

08:21.300 --> 08:22.260
Among us,

08:23.220 --> 08:24.660
some are dead,

08:26.660 --> 08:27.500
and some are maimed.

08:29.580 --> 08:30.540
Yet who caused all this?

08:30.540 --> 08:32.300
Was it Nie Hengcheng? Or...

08:38.740 --> 08:40.260
Now, they are all dead.

08:41.660 --> 08:42.500
Tell me.

08:43.700 --> 08:44.740
Who can I blame?

08:48.460 --> 08:49.780
Who can I hate?

08:54.460 --> 08:55.300
Xiuming,

08:55.860 --> 08:56.700
tomorrow,

08:56.940 --> 08:57.900
Xiaofeng and I

08:59.060 --> 09:00.460
will leave Qingque Sect.

09:18.660 --> 09:19.500
Tomorrow,

09:20.140 --> 09:21.500
I'll leave with Lord Cai.

09:22.780 --> 09:23.620
After this,

09:23.980 --> 09:25.460
let's forget each other.

09:26.620 --> 09:27.780
We won't meet again.

09:28.500 --> 09:30.020
We have treasures across the lands.

09:30.860 --> 09:32.340
- You...
- Donate them, please.

09:33.027 --> 09:34.607
I've loved literature, not martial arts.

09:34.860 --> 09:37.700
This life, being a teacher is enough.

09:38.860 --> 09:39.700
Even with a fortune,

09:39.700 --> 09:40.780
I'm still powerless.

09:40.959 --> 09:42.939
Perhaps it's a misfortune
rather than a blessing.

09:43.540 --> 09:44.580
An innocent man bears guilt

09:44.900 --> 09:46.160
because of the jewel he carries.

09:47.140 --> 09:47.980
Fine.

09:48.260 --> 09:49.340
Then, as he hoped,

09:50.460 --> 09:51.380
be an ordinary person.

09:52.020 --> 09:52.860
I heard

09:53.820 --> 09:55.033
that before Qiu Yuanfeng died,

09:55.900 --> 09:56.740
you asked him.

09:57.500 --> 09:58.340
Was it him?

09:58.740 --> 10:00.140
The culprit may be someone else.

10:01.740 --> 10:03.180
I'll find him

10:05.180 --> 10:06.420
and cut him into pieces.

10:15.100 --> 10:16.260
Your parents are gone.

10:16.500 --> 10:17.940
I should've stayed for a few days,

10:18.540 --> 10:19.940
but my wife is ill.

10:20.060 --> 10:21.300
I must return to care for her.

10:22.020 --> 10:22.860
Zhao,

10:23.500 --> 10:25.180
Jianghu erupts again.

10:25.780 --> 10:27.820
With the successive tragedies.

10:28.940 --> 10:30.300
You and Yuqi's marriage

10:31.220 --> 10:32.340
should be arranged.

10:40.140 --> 10:40.980
Uncle Zhou,

10:41.860 --> 10:44.260
I still haven't figured everything out.

10:45.300 --> 10:47.340
I know you still think about Ms. Luo,

10:48.060 --> 10:49.740
but years of battle have caused

10:49.740 --> 10:50.940
countless deaths and injuries.

10:51.140 --> 10:53.580
Many things can't be judged
by normal logic.

10:53.860 --> 10:54.860
However deep you probe,

10:55.300 --> 10:57.500
those who left will not return.

10:58.220 --> 10:59.620
The sooner you marry Yuqi,

10:59.940 --> 11:01.066
the sooner your parents and I

11:01.260 --> 11:02.420
can rest easy.

11:04.780 --> 11:05.820
If Aunt were here,

11:08.340 --> 11:09.780
would she just stand by?

11:21.500 --> 11:22.340
She wouldn't,

11:23.540 --> 11:24.380
but she'd hope

11:24.860 --> 11:26.060
you would.

11:27.500 --> 11:29.300
She arranged your betrothal with Yuqi

11:30.140 --> 11:31.060
to keep you

11:31.620 --> 11:33.620
from Jianghu disputes.

11:43.940 --> 11:44.780
Master.

11:47.020 --> 11:47.860
Zhao,

11:49.020 --> 11:50.900
after finishing the memorial,

11:50.980 --> 11:52.020
I came

11:52.020 --> 11:52.860
to see you

11:52.860 --> 11:53.700
and Ning.

11:55.260 --> 11:56.100
Where is Zhou?

11:56.300 --> 11:57.140
He just left.

11:57.151 --> 11:58.433
He always wants to trick you

11:58.444 --> 12:00.300
into going to Peiqiong Manor.

12:00.780 --> 12:01.620
I really feared

12:02.220 --> 12:03.420
you might go with him.

12:03.980 --> 12:05.300
Master, rest assured.

12:05.660 --> 12:06.500
Now that I'm here,

12:06.900 --> 12:08.060
I'll stay for a whole year.

12:08.980 --> 12:11.020
Keep your word.

12:13.780 --> 12:14.620
Ning,

12:15.780 --> 12:16.940
I didn't expect you

12:17.540 --> 12:19.900
to recognize Thunderstorm at a glance.

12:22.300 --> 12:23.900
Watch out! It's Thunderstorm!

12:30.020 --> 12:31.380
My father told me.

12:32.660 --> 12:33.700
So did my aunt.

12:35.300 --> 12:37.220
I never expected
a random demon sect weapon

12:37.220 --> 12:38.060
to be so deadly.

12:38.260 --> 12:39.380
The demon sect is brutal.

12:40.060 --> 12:41.340
You've never experienced it.

12:42.340 --> 12:43.180
I hope

12:44.140 --> 12:45.780
you never will.

12:51.820 --> 12:52.940
That's also Aunt's wish.

12:55.420 --> 12:56.260
Rest early.

12:56.660 --> 12:57.500
I'll take my leave.

13:22.260 --> 13:23.100
Zhao.

13:23.660 --> 13:25.500
Why are you practicing alone today?

13:25.780 --> 13:27.060
After the memorial,

13:27.140 --> 13:29.030
everyone was deeply shaken,

13:29.260 --> 13:30.520
both angry and confused.

13:30.940 --> 13:32.530
They felt unable to focus,

13:32.660 --> 13:33.970
unsure of the path ahead.

13:34.100 --> 13:36.500
So, Yuzhi let them return
to calm themselves.

13:36.900 --> 13:38.580
Then why do you keep practicing?

13:38.580 --> 13:40.580
Martial arts exist to uphold justice.

13:41.300 --> 13:42.820
Whether others act wrongly or not,

13:43.060 --> 13:44.940
upholding justice itself is not wrong.

13:45.540 --> 13:46.460
As long as it is right,

13:46.820 --> 13:47.940
I won't regret it.

13:49.980 --> 13:50.820
Yes.

13:51.740 --> 13:53.220
Aunt also said this.

13:54.340 --> 13:56.780
There's nothing in life to regret.

13:57.540 --> 13:58.660
If you think it's right,

13:59.180 --> 14:00.020
do it.

14:01.780 --> 14:02.620
Zhao!

14:04.900 --> 14:05.900
What do you need?

14:06.420 --> 14:08.580
I just went to do acupuncture for Chang.

14:08.580 --> 14:09.540
Why isn't he there?

14:15.100 --> 14:16.220
Master already suspects you.

14:17.820 --> 14:19.300
You can't continue to stay.

14:24.660 --> 14:25.580
Let's part here.

14:30.220 --> 14:31.060
Okay.

15:58.700 --> 15:59.606
All have taken poison.

16:00.900 --> 16:02.020
The Demonic Camp.

16:03.500 --> 16:04.700
You didn't kill them?

16:05.086 --> 16:06.966
An insider killed
the cliff-guarding disciples,

16:07.140 --> 16:08.380
leading the Demonic Camp here.

16:08.660 --> 16:09.820
Before the swords were drawn,

16:09.940 --> 16:11.540
they were ambushed and killed,

16:12.020 --> 16:13.020
completely unprepared.

16:13.700 --> 16:15.380
To kill 8 disciples simultaneously,

16:16.300 --> 16:17.720
there must be more than one insider.

16:20.140 --> 16:21.420
The sword marks are curved.

16:23.460 --> 16:24.446
Aunt said the 13th move

16:24.780 --> 16:26.460
of the Taichu Swordsmanship

16:26.940 --> 16:28.340
requires a lower body,

16:28.620 --> 16:29.540
an upward thrust,

16:30.060 --> 16:31.140
and hilt rotation

16:32.060 --> 16:33.340
after piercing into one's body.

16:38.270 --> 16:39.140
Oh, no.

16:39.180 --> 16:40.700
Wu Gang and Wu Xiong of Taichu Temple

16:40.711 --> 16:41.660
are recuperating here.

16:46.860 --> 16:47.700
And you left?

16:52.060 --> 16:52.900
Forget it.

16:54.260 --> 16:55.100
Let it be.

17:16.940 --> 17:18.126
These volumes of mindful ways

17:18.980 --> 17:21.140
were gifts from your brother long ago.

17:25.540 --> 17:27.540
Alas, the times have changed.

17:31.980 --> 17:32.820
Master, be careful!

17:41.060 --> 17:42.500
Master!

17:48.940 --> 17:49.860
Master,

17:50.453 --> 17:51.420
this dagger is poisoned.

17:51.540 --> 17:52.380
I guessed it,

17:53.300 --> 17:54.900
so I sealed the acupoints beforehand.

17:55.340 --> 17:57.426
Later, I'll force out the poison,
and I'll be fine.

18:00.300 --> 18:01.980
Master, this is Wu Xiong.

18:02.260 --> 18:03.100
Where is Wu Gang?

18:05.140 --> 18:07.460
Wu Gang went to pay respects to Mr. Wu.

18:08.980 --> 18:10.060
I let Yuzhi go with him.

18:11.500 --> 18:12.340
Oh, no.

18:12.900 --> 18:13.940
Yuzhi is in danger.

18:14.220 --> 18:15.660
Master, heal first.

18:15.700 --> 18:16.540
I'll go save him.

18:45.140 --> 18:46.820
We've treated you both well.

18:47.740 --> 18:49.580
Why collude with the demon sect

18:49.820 --> 18:51.100
to commit such vile acts?

18:51.620 --> 18:52.573
Stop talking nonsense.

18:53.460 --> 18:55.700
If it weren't
for your grandfather's selfishness,

18:56.060 --> 18:58.180
refusing to use Elder Kaiyang
to save my brother,

18:58.940 --> 19:00.700
he wouldn't have ended up

19:00.700 --> 19:02.260
like that.

19:03.740 --> 19:05.500
What a so-called greatest sect.

19:06.580 --> 19:08.580
What a hypocrite.

19:09.020 --> 19:10.780
I did nothing to Mr. Wu.

19:11.220 --> 19:12.540
Why do this to me?

19:13.260 --> 19:15.300
Because you are Yin's grandson.

19:15.900 --> 19:16.820
You deserve death too.

19:18.980 --> 19:20.460
You've been hit by my Nether Aura.

19:21.340 --> 19:22.340
Even if you don't die,

19:22.700 --> 19:23.900
you'll be invalid.

19:24.420 --> 19:25.260
Attack!

19:39.420 --> 19:40.260
Xiong's blade!

19:40.940 --> 19:41.860
Qi Yunke is not dead!

19:42.460 --> 19:43.300
My master is fine!

19:44.340 --> 19:45.180
Zhao, go now.

19:45.260 --> 19:46.100
Don't worry about me.

19:46.540 --> 19:47.380
As long as I live,

19:48.100 --> 19:48.940
I won't let you die.

19:58.340 --> 19:59.260
Sunshine Blade.

20:05.140 --> 20:06.300
My Sunshine Blade

20:06.900 --> 20:09.300
once killed Nie Hengcheng, your chief.

20:09.580 --> 20:10.700
If you want to test it,

20:12.340 --> 20:13.180
come!

20:16.060 --> 20:16.900
Attack!

21:14.100 --> 21:14.940
Zhao!

21:41.140 --> 21:41.980
You didn't leave.

21:46.020 --> 21:46.900
My Smiley is spilled.

21:48.660 --> 21:49.500
You owe me a pack.

21:51.460 --> 21:53.700
Why protect Yin Dai's grandson?

21:54.380 --> 21:55.660
If not for Yin Dai,

21:56.140 --> 21:58.100
Cai Pingshu wouldn't have died.

21:59.380 --> 22:00.220
What did you say?

22:01.500 --> 22:02.340
Back then,

22:02.940 --> 22:05.820
he deliberately...

22:10.260 --> 22:11.100
Yuzhi!

22:12.100 --> 22:12.940
Yuzhi!

22:13.380 --> 22:14.220
Are you okay?

22:14.300 --> 22:15.140
Yuzhi.

22:15.620 --> 22:16.460
Finish it.

22:27.620 --> 22:28.460
Wait a moment.

22:28.500 --> 22:29.340
Alright.

22:29.380 --> 22:30.220
How is it?

22:31.100 --> 22:32.620
- How are you?
- I'm fine.

22:32.660 --> 22:34.060
Here, drink the medicine.

22:35.780 --> 22:36.620
Endure it.

22:42.520 --> 22:43.746
Cold poison entered the veins;

22:43.757 --> 22:45.003
his internal energy was damaged.

22:46.380 --> 22:47.940
Yuzhi is afflicted by Nether Aura.

22:49.940 --> 22:50.820
I never expected

22:51.420 --> 22:52.260
Wu Gang to have

22:52.940 --> 22:54.580
such a sinister martial skill.

22:55.740 --> 22:56.580
Xiuming,

22:57.460 --> 22:58.380
how confident are you?

22:59.620 --> 23:01.860
Wenxun is suppressing his cold poison.

23:02.740 --> 23:03.580
However,

23:04.140 --> 23:05.340
even if controlled,

23:05.620 --> 23:07.940
Yuzhi's power is left at less than 30%.

23:10.700 --> 23:12.620
Father, save Yuzhi!

23:12.620 --> 23:14.020
He must not die!

23:14.020 --> 23:15.100
Stop yelling!

23:15.220 --> 23:17.460
If you keep yelling, Yuzhi will be gone.

23:23.780 --> 23:24.620
Xingjia,

23:25.480 --> 23:26.440
tell all sects

23:26.620 --> 23:27.580
to be vigilant,

23:27.860 --> 23:29.220
lest the demon sect ambush them.

23:30.060 --> 23:30.900
Yes.

23:43.940 --> 23:47.140
He deliberately...

23:56.900 --> 23:57.740
Pingchun!

23:58.380 --> 23:59.220
Pingchun!

23:59.780 --> 24:01.140
Come and save her!

24:01.380 --> 24:02.220
Come!

24:02.860 --> 24:03.700
Hurry!

24:06.420 --> 24:08.500
Those cold-blooded hypocrites

24:09.660 --> 24:11.100
just stood by.

24:40.180 --> 24:42.060
You've been overly protected
by your family.

24:43.500 --> 24:44.540
Once outside,

24:45.660 --> 24:46.580
harden your heart.

24:47.340 --> 24:48.180
I know.

24:49.420 --> 24:50.900
Life and death are common.

24:51.620 --> 24:52.500
If someone is killed,

24:53.060 --> 24:54.020
someone must pay.

24:55.500 --> 24:56.460
Spare a villain,

24:57.460 --> 24:59.020
and more innocents suffer.

24:59.780 --> 25:01.740
Aunt trained me tirelessly
in martial arts,

25:02.420 --> 25:03.660
so I could one day

25:04.980 --> 25:07.460
protect myself and others.

25:07.660 --> 25:08.540
Ms. Cai's plan for you

25:09.860 --> 25:10.900
was also far-reaching.

25:11.980 --> 25:14.180
But I didn't protect Master and Yuzhi.

25:15.300 --> 25:16.140
However strong,

25:17.620 --> 25:18.860
one may still be overwhelmed.

25:19.900 --> 25:20.860
We can only do our best.

25:23.260 --> 25:24.100
Yes.

25:26.140 --> 25:27.160
We can only do our best.

25:30.940 --> 25:31.900
Aren't you leaving?

25:32.113 --> 25:33.060
Why are you still here?

25:38.700 --> 25:40.140
The ones who attacked Qingque Sect

25:40.333 --> 25:41.660
were also from the Demonic Camp.

25:41.959 --> 25:43.453
I want to find them and take revenge.

25:46.340 --> 25:47.260
Lord Qi,

25:47.660 --> 25:49.620
feeling guilty toward Ms. Luo,

25:50.140 --> 25:51.940
let those two recover here.

25:53.420 --> 25:55.500
This must also be
part of the demon sect's plan.

25:56.380 --> 25:57.900
A subtle line

25:58.100 --> 25:59.220
runs through.

26:00.460 --> 26:01.820
Ms. Luo came here

26:01.940 --> 26:03.740
but brought these two pawns.

26:04.940 --> 26:06.500
Did Ms. Luo...

26:07.420 --> 26:08.540
She didn't know.

26:10.260 --> 26:11.660
She must've been used.

26:18.700 --> 26:22.260
(A few days later, Chuitian Dock)

26:24.180 --> 26:25.020
Yuzhi,

26:25.740 --> 26:26.960
this is Longjiao Incense

26:27.140 --> 26:28.060
for calming the spirit.

26:30.500 --> 26:31.580
And this is

26:32.100 --> 26:33.140
Blood Swallow Congee.

26:33.420 --> 26:34.700
Grandfather left this.

26:34.980 --> 26:36.260
It helps replenish qi.

26:41.100 --> 26:41.940
Yuzhi?

26:42.140 --> 26:42.980
Lingbo,

26:45.740 --> 26:46.980
I want to be alone for a while.

26:51.660 --> 26:52.660
Yuzhi,

26:53.780 --> 26:56.140
I know you feel uneasy,

26:56.740 --> 26:57.660
but rest assured.

26:57.820 --> 26:59.020
I heard from Uncle Lei

26:59.300 --> 27:01.460
that once Father uses
Tianhuo Dragon Aura

27:01.460 --> 27:02.680
to channel energy and heal you,

27:02.820 --> 27:03.833
combined with these herbs,

27:03.940 --> 27:05.860
your martial arts will slowly recover.

27:11.980 --> 27:12.980
Yuzhi,

27:18.580 --> 27:19.980
you're blaming me.

27:21.020 --> 27:23.220
You think
I shouldn't have killed Wu Gang?

27:25.180 --> 27:26.420
But if I hadn't,

27:26.420 --> 27:27.540
would he have been allowed

27:27.540 --> 27:28.780
to defame Grandfather?

27:29.340 --> 27:30.220
Cai Zhao

27:30.380 --> 27:31.900
always likes to stir up trouble.

27:32.206 --> 27:33.220
If she had heard about it,

27:33.220 --> 27:34.373
she'd have caused more chaos.

27:34.660 --> 27:36.020
Forget the past.

27:38.860 --> 27:39.700
Yes.

27:41.380 --> 27:42.380
Recovery comes first.

27:43.980 --> 27:44.820
Yuzhi,

27:45.150 --> 27:47.183
Nanny Mao prepared a herbal bath
in the hot spring,

27:47.300 --> 27:48.700
specially using Grandfather's

27:48.700 --> 27:50.260
Revival Pill.

27:50.490 --> 27:51.340
Let's go.

27:51.380 --> 27:52.220
I'll take you.

27:52.740 --> 27:53.580
No need.

27:55.520 --> 27:56.860
It's been carefully prepared.

27:59.260 --> 28:00.100
Let's go.

28:00.420 --> 28:01.260
No need.

28:03.460 --> 28:04.300
Lingbo.

28:04.960 --> 28:06.390
Lingbo has been sincere with you,

28:06.660 --> 28:07.806
planning all this for you.

28:07.817 --> 28:08.923
And you treat her like this?

28:09.140 --> 28:10.060
Fengchi,

28:10.530 --> 28:11.740
Yuzhi didn't mean it.

28:12.060 --> 28:12.900
I'm fine.

28:14.346 --> 28:15.652
I want to recover in peace alone.

28:16.540 --> 28:17.500
Please go out first.

28:21.060 --> 28:21.900
Yuzhi,

28:22.780 --> 28:23.820
I'm your senior brother.

28:24.460 --> 28:25.700
Today, just listen to me

28:26.220 --> 28:27.300
and go with Lingbo to heal.

28:30.300 --> 28:31.340
What's the matter, Fengchi?

28:32.700 --> 28:34.180
Usually, you can't beat Yuzhi,

28:34.340 --> 28:36.180
so today,
taking advantage of his injury,

28:36.220 --> 28:37.366
you show off your power, huh?

28:39.413 --> 28:39.925
Cai Zhao,

28:39.936 --> 28:41.100
what nonsense are you saying?

28:41.100 --> 28:42.300
Yeah, that's nonsense.

28:43.100 --> 28:44.380
Stop stirring trouble here.

28:44.500 --> 28:46.380
We're just here to check on Yuzhi.

28:46.780 --> 28:47.620
Lingbo,

28:48.620 --> 28:49.460
if nothing else,

28:50.860 --> 28:52.500
you and Fengchi may leave.

28:57.380 --> 28:58.220
Lingbo.

29:04.140 --> 29:05.486
Lately, I've been recovering here,

29:05.723 --> 29:06.966
so I haven't been able to visit.

29:07.546 --> 29:08.940
Thank you both for saving my life.

29:10.420 --> 29:11.380
Your eyes

29:11.740 --> 29:12.606
are better now, right?

29:13.420 --> 29:14.260
Yeah.

29:14.860 --> 29:15.760
Yuzhi,

29:15.760 --> 29:16.820
I came to tell you:

29:17.460 --> 29:18.370
My aunt's friend

29:18.380 --> 29:19.700
was once afflicted by Nether Aura

29:20.100 --> 29:20.980
but later recovered.

29:21.260 --> 29:22.100
Really?

29:22.220 --> 29:23.060
Really.

29:23.300 --> 29:24.140
How did it happen?

29:24.700 --> 29:27.180
Apparently, my aunt found
a special herb.

29:29.060 --> 29:30.580
I already sent a letter to my parents.

29:30.940 --> 29:32.660
It should reach them in a few days.

29:33.980 --> 29:34.820
Thank you.

29:36.340 --> 29:38.900
Something's wrong!

29:39.340 --> 29:40.660
After leaving, all sects

29:40.660 --> 29:41.940
were ambushed by the demon sect.

29:41.940 --> 29:42.780
What?

29:42.980 --> 29:45.020
Lord Song went to Yangzhou
to buy a golden tortoise

29:45.180 --> 29:46.020
and avoided it.

29:48.060 --> 29:49.380
Taichu Temple broke apart halfway;

29:49.486 --> 29:51.035
Siqi Sect diverted to marry a concubine.

29:51.140 --> 29:51.980
They also avoided it.

29:54.620 --> 29:55.569
What about my parents?

29:55.580 --> 29:56.940
Mr. Cai's group moved slowly,

29:57.340 --> 29:58.413
so they weren't ambushed.

29:59.946 --> 30:00.692
But Peiqiong Manor

30:00.703 --> 30:02.226
collided directly with the demon sect.

30:02.340 --> 30:03.380
Lord Zhou was injured.

30:03.700 --> 30:04.540
How severe?

30:05.660 --> 30:07.220
Minor scratches.

30:07.660 --> 30:08.780
Yuqi is also fine.

30:09.100 --> 30:10.340
They've returned to the manor.

30:11.780 --> 30:12.620
Fan,

30:13.100 --> 30:14.700
can you speak in one go?

30:15.180 --> 30:16.220
Look at Zhao, so scared.

30:19.940 --> 30:20.780
Right.

30:20.900 --> 30:22.020
Uncle Li said

30:22.020 --> 30:23.540
we must strengthen defenses

30:23.700 --> 30:25.180
and invited many external elites.

30:25.620 --> 30:26.460
Zhao,

30:26.500 --> 30:27.340
you know arrays.

30:27.780 --> 30:29.100
Tomorrow morning, accompany me

30:29.173 --> 30:31.159
to Qingque Town to collect
some array materials.

30:33.180 --> 30:34.740
It seems traveling is getting harder.

30:37.300 --> 30:38.140
Ning,

30:39.140 --> 30:39.980
what's your plan?

30:40.780 --> 30:41.820
I'll go down with you.

30:43.659 --> 30:44.799
There are about to be changes

30:45.740 --> 30:46.820
in Qingque Sect.

31:06.380 --> 31:07.460
If you like it,

31:08.260 --> 31:09.580
maybe there's still a chance...

31:09.580 --> 31:10.420
No need.

31:12.060 --> 31:13.060
After you leave,

31:13.300 --> 31:14.340
go handle your affairs.

31:14.899 --> 31:15.965
Only when free from worries

31:16.146 --> 31:17.453
can you succeed in all endeavors.

31:24.420 --> 31:25.260
Breeze?

31:26.220 --> 31:27.420
I heard from Fan

31:27.740 --> 31:28.860
that before your mother left,

31:29.500 --> 31:30.986
she took the last three jars of Breeze

31:30.997 --> 31:31.940
from the wine cellar.

31:32.940 --> 31:34.060
This is the last jar.

31:34.660 --> 31:35.780
I got it from Uncle Lei.

31:36.820 --> 31:38.220
I promised you before

31:38.580 --> 31:39.420
to protect you

31:39.820 --> 31:41.220
and not let you face

31:41.820 --> 31:42.660
revenge alone.

31:43.260 --> 31:44.673
Now, I fear I'll break that promise.

31:46.873 --> 31:47.780
Please don't blame me.

31:53.820 --> 31:54.660
I won't.

32:05.940 --> 32:07.540
When Mr. Chang died because of me,

32:09.940 --> 32:11.340
I was filled with hatred.

32:12.540 --> 32:13.620
All I wanted was revenge.

32:16.100 --> 32:16.940
But unexpectedly,

32:17.660 --> 32:18.500
in just a few months,

32:19.060 --> 32:19.900
I met you

32:20.980 --> 32:21.980
and experienced things

32:22.220 --> 32:23.460
I never had before.

32:23.660 --> 32:24.500
It's my fortune.

32:25.900 --> 32:26.740
Thank you.

32:30.820 --> 32:31.660
Zhao, rest assured.

32:33.020 --> 32:34.220
I'll avenge the Chang family,

32:34.980 --> 32:35.820
my father,

32:36.700 --> 32:37.740
and myself.

32:44.740 --> 32:45.600
Chang Ning,

32:45.610 --> 32:46.540
no matter who it's for,

32:46.860 --> 32:47.700
you swore

32:48.220 --> 32:49.580
never to use the Disintegration.

32:50.220 --> 32:51.060
Your life

32:51.340 --> 32:52.326
was saved by Uncle Chang,

32:53.020 --> 32:53.860
Uncle Lei,

32:54.540 --> 32:55.380
Jiang Ning,

32:55.580 --> 32:56.420
and me,

32:56.540 --> 32:57.980
through great effort.

32:58.980 --> 32:59.820
Survive.

33:00.900 --> 33:02.140
Find every way to survive.

33:03.580 --> 33:04.580
If injured,

33:05.180 --> 33:06.060
come back here.

33:10.860 --> 33:11.780
Come to Luoying Valley.

33:12.706 --> 33:13.813
My mother is a great healer.

33:14.140 --> 33:14.990
She's as good

33:15.000 --> 33:15.880
as Uncle Lei.

33:17.500 --> 33:18.340
Sure.

33:23.420 --> 33:25.020
You told me to survive no matter what,

33:26.833 --> 33:27.986
but you should also remember:

33:29.780 --> 33:31.180
No matter when or where,

33:32.260 --> 33:33.140
finish things

33:34.380 --> 33:35.220
when necessary.

33:36.100 --> 33:36.940
Otherwise,

33:37.220 --> 33:38.140
lingering attachments

33:39.540 --> 33:40.620
will lead to ruin.

33:49.860 --> 33:50.700
I'll remember.

34:03.860 --> 34:06.580
(Disciples' Dorm)

34:06.580 --> 34:07.420
Xingjia!

34:13.660 --> 34:14.500
Xingjia?

34:15.860 --> 34:16.700
He's not here.

34:20.180 --> 34:21.020
Zhuang,

34:22.180 --> 34:23.020
where's Xingjia?

34:23.226 --> 34:24.580
I looked for him at the Mao hour,

34:24.580 --> 34:25.420
and he wasn't here.

34:25.940 --> 34:26.966
Did he go to Qingque Town?

34:27.580 --> 34:29.500
(Zhuang Shu)
He said yesterday he'd go there.

34:35.020 --> 34:36.106
Xingjia must be in trouble.

34:36.838 --> 34:38.412
He comes from a wealthy merchant family,

34:38.660 --> 34:39.500
a proper gentleman.

34:39.860 --> 34:41.660
He'd follow the routine
of making the bed,

34:42.300 --> 34:43.140
but look at this bed.

34:43.873 --> 34:45.239
He must've been taken by someone.

34:51.540 --> 34:52.380
Zhao,

34:52.740 --> 34:53.580
have you noticed?

34:53.860 --> 34:54.820
Since just now,

34:55.660 --> 34:56.940
someone has been watching us.

35:01.220 --> 35:02.060
Don't tell anyone

35:03.540 --> 35:04.380
about Fan yet.

35:07.540 --> 35:08.500
Since he's gone,

35:09.980 --> 35:10.860
let's go without him.

35:11.700 --> 35:12.540
Let's go.

35:15.140 --> 35:16.260
After the memorial,

35:16.766 --> 35:18.639
(Qingque Town)
many martial artists came here.

35:19.580 --> 35:20.780
Finding Fan

35:21.660 --> 35:23.100
won't be easy.

35:24.100 --> 35:25.700
Outer disciples guard the town gate.

35:26.260 --> 35:27.660
Xingjia should still be in town.

35:28.300 --> 35:29.500
The inn is full of people,

35:29.813 --> 35:31.282
not a suitable place to hide someone.

35:31.660 --> 35:32.500
I think

35:33.220 --> 35:35.060
he's hiding in a civilian house.

35:36.020 --> 35:37.322
There must be at least 100 houses

35:37.333 --> 35:38.340
in Qingque Town.

35:39.140 --> 35:41.340
If we search recklessly,
it'll alert the enemy.

35:49.980 --> 35:50.820
I have a plan.

35:55.300 --> 35:56.140
Coming.

35:58.460 --> 35:59.820
Miss, what's the matter?

36:00.300 --> 36:01.420
I'm Cuihua, new here.

36:02.540 --> 36:04.660
Last night, my mother
gave birth to a sister.

36:05.260 --> 36:07.260
My father said I should deliver
celebratory eggs.

36:09.940 --> 36:11.820
Miss, in Qingque Town,

36:11.900 --> 36:13.786
celebratory eggs must be given
in even numbers.

36:14.860 --> 36:16.020
I just moved here.

36:16.091 --> 36:17.080
I didn't know the custom.

36:17.260 --> 36:18.140
Here's another one.

36:18.740 --> 36:19.580
Thank you.

36:20.660 --> 36:21.700
Take care, miss.

36:25.570 --> 36:26.420
Who is it?

36:26.460 --> 36:27.853
I came to deliver celebratory eggs.

36:29.180 --> 36:30.460
My mother gave birth to a sister.

36:30.540 --> 36:32.380
Father said to deliver eggs.

36:32.470 --> 36:33.499
Good things come in pairs.

36:34.500 --> 36:36.700
- Who is it?
- I came to deliver eggs.

36:39.580 --> 36:40.420
Thank you.

36:50.560 --> 36:51.619
He doesn't know the custom.

36:51.860 --> 36:52.700
He must be new here.

36:52.860 --> 36:54.540
He has sharp eyes
and long-lasting energy.

36:55.100 --> 36:55.940
He must be a master.

37:25.620 --> 37:26.460
Xingjia.

37:32.933 --> 37:34.940
(Qian Xueshen)
Are you trying to tire me to death?

37:34.940 --> 37:36.700
Even a mule needs a break.

37:36.900 --> 37:38.160
These past 15 days have drained

37:38.171 --> 37:38.951
all my power.

37:39.086 --> 37:40.175
I just rested for two days,

37:40.186 --> 37:40.940
and you came again.

37:41.180 --> 37:42.260
Mr. Qian, don't worry.

37:42.660 --> 37:44.140
We wouldn't want to exhaust you.

37:44.780 --> 37:46.353
This time, it doesn't require precision.

37:46.580 --> 37:47.820
Please, Mr. Qian,

37:48.140 --> 37:49.020
do your job.

37:59.540 --> 38:01.180
He looks delicate

38:01.740 --> 38:02.633
and has fragile bones.

38:03.620 --> 38:04.980
He doesn't seem to be an elite.

38:06.420 --> 38:07.746
Why do you want to transform him?

38:08.100 --> 38:09.540
This kid is cunning,

38:10.100 --> 38:11.660
sneaking into the Disciples' Dorm

38:11.660 --> 38:12.700
at night to check luggage.

38:12.999 --> 38:14.213
If not replaced with our own...

38:15.060 --> 38:15.900
Enough.

38:16.220 --> 38:17.060
Mr. Qian,

38:17.260 --> 38:18.100
get to work.

38:36.420 --> 38:37.260
I'll transform you.

39:12.700 --> 39:13.780
The Face Shift.

39:14.740 --> 39:15.780
It reappears.

39:16.700 --> 39:17.540
You know again?

39:18.380 --> 39:19.220
Don't look at me.

39:19.300 --> 39:20.260
It's not my business.

39:20.900 --> 39:22.580
The Body Shift is indeed wondrous,

39:22.940 --> 39:23.820
perfectly executed.

39:24.220 --> 39:25.220
This person can be killed

39:25.900 --> 39:26.953
to prevent future trouble.

39:33.460 --> 39:34.500
Please, spare me!

39:37.300 --> 39:38.140
He just fainted?

39:40.780 --> 39:41.660
Such a waste.

39:42.460 --> 39:43.300
I'll chop him up.

39:43.540 --> 39:44.540
I'm awake!

39:45.460 --> 39:46.300
I'm awake.

39:46.620 --> 39:47.460
I'm awake.

39:48.500 --> 39:50.073
What's your connection to Qianmian Sect?

39:50.260 --> 39:51.100
Who are you?

39:51.460 --> 39:53.380
I'm Qian Xueshen,

39:53.420 --> 39:55.340
the last descendant of Qianmian Sect.

39:55.660 --> 39:56.540
Please understand.

39:56.940 --> 39:58.140
They forced me to do this.

39:58.340 --> 40:00.020
I'm just a scholar,

40:00.220 --> 40:01.195
with elders and children

40:01.206 --> 40:01.900
to care about.

40:09.680 --> 40:20.340
=Generation to Generation=

40:39.100 --> 40:43.510
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

40:44.075 --> 40:48.690
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

40:49.030 --> 40:53.595
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

40:54.120 --> 40:58.420
♪Free to wander in the world♪

41:01.365 --> 41:06.065
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

41:06.590 --> 41:10.880
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

41:11.540 --> 41:15.570
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

41:15.885 --> 41:21.010
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

41:21.585 --> 41:26.395
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

41:26.610 --> 41:30.780
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

41:31.505 --> 41:35.440
♪I freely roam in the world♪

41:35.940 --> 41:41.215
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

42:03.945 --> 42:09.075
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

42:09.440 --> 42:13.810
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

42:14.075 --> 42:18.205
♪I freely roam in the world♪

42:18.390 --> 42:23.965
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
